name: Burnout
description: This is a representation of when I have a lot of assignments or things to do but at the same time, I'm already mentally exhausted and feeling empty. Energy is already drained and just want to disappear and not have any contact with people. A lot of words stuck in my head like "Oh come on I have to finish this" "Can I finish this?", "Ugh, please god I just want to rest"...
